for (i in 1:((nrow(Vol_data_2)-w)/5)){
  
  cont=matrix(0,4,4)
  
  cont[1,2]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/

             sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0)!=0)
  
  cont[2,1]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/
                 rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0))/

  cont[1,3]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/
                 rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0))/
             sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0)!=0)
  
  cont[3,1]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/
                 rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0))/
             sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Europe",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0)!=0)
  
  cont[2,3]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/
                 rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0))/
             sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0)!=0)
  
  cont[3,2]= sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])])/
                 rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0))/
             sum(rowSums(Con_Matrices_2[[i]][grep("Asia",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4]),grep("North America",plot_info[match(colnames(Con_Matrices_2[[i]]),names2),4])]!=0)!=0)
  
   cont[which(is.nan(cont))]<-0
  
  #To others
  cont[1,4]= sum(cont[1,2],cont[1,3])
  cont[2,4]= sum(cont[2,1],cont[2,3])
  cont[3,4]= sum(cont[3,1],cont[3,2])

  #From others
  cont[4,1]= sum(cont[2,1],cont[3,1])
  cont[4,2]= sum(cont[1,2],cont[3,2])
  cont[4,3]= sum(cont[1,3],cont[2,3])

  
  #Total Con
  cont[4,4]= sum(colSums(Con_Matrices[[i]]))
  
  Cont_con[[i]]=cont
}

Only evaluate the Top-n of spillover linkages

Create a function for this

nlargest <- function(m, n, sim = TRUE) {
  mult <- 1;
  if (sim) mult <- 2;
  res <- order(m, decreasing = TRUE)[seq_len(n) * mult];
  pos <- arrayInd(res, dim(m), useNames = TRUE);
  list(values = m[res],
       position = pos)
}

TopN= vector("list",(nrow(Vol_data_2)-w)/5)

  TopN[[i]]= nlargest(Con_Matrices_2[[i]],250)
}

}
